Certainly, here are five example sentences in Serbian that use the word "nedostajati" in different forms and positions:

1. *Nedostaje* mi tvoj glas. (I miss your voice.)
2. Koliko još *nedostaje* do kraja godine? (How much longer until the end of the year?)
3. Njemu *nedostaje* hrabrosti da prizna istinu. (He lacks the courage to admit the truth.)
4. *Nedostajalo* joj je vreme da završi sve zadatke. (She was short on time to finish all the tasks.)
5. Ono što *nedostaje* ovom gradu je veći broj zelenih površina. (What this city lacks is a larger number of green spaces.)

Note: The asterisk (*) marks the word "nedostajati" in each sentence.